subtitleNullable: A six years dataset of daily weather report of Kolkata, from 2017 to 2022.
descriptionNullable:
The data set contains the daily weather report of the city of Kolkata, India. There are two versions of this data set. The first data set includes the weather report **from 2017 to 2021** and the second data set includes the weather report **from 2017 to 2022**. There are **25 data columns**.
This data has been fetched using *Visual Crossing Weather API* from *RapidAPI*.

The columns of this data set are 
1. 'Address', 
2. 'Date time', 
3. 'Minimum Temperature',
4. 'Maximum Temperature', 
5. 'Temperature', 
6. 'Dew Point', 
7. 'Relative Humidity', 
8. 'Heat Index', 
9. 'Wind Speed', 
10. 'Wind Gust', 
11. 'Wind Direction', 
12. 'Wind Chill', 
13. 'Precipitation', 
14. 'Precipitation Cover', 
15. 'Snow Depth', 
16. 'Visibility', 
17. 'Cloud Cover', 
18. 'Sea Level Pressure', 
19. 'Weather Type', 
20. 'Latitude', 
21. 'Longitude', 
22. 'Resolved Address', 
23. 'Name', 
24. 'Info', 
25. 'Conditions'


Six years of daily weather reports( in CSV format) of Kolkata, a West Bengal city in India.
